Name: 50 Level Survival
About the game: 50 Level Survival is a point and click casual adventure game in which the goal is to make it to the end. The game gets progressively harder and you make it through the levels. Kill the enemies to level up your character and use the resources you have at your disposal to make it through the 50 Levels to reign supreme. Are you up for the task?
